            <FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Lucida Grande,Geneva,Arial">
            Here are some tips to optimize performance of the software and OpenGL renderer versions of Quake:
           <TABLE BORDER="0" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="3">
                <TR VALIGN="top">
                    <TD WIDTH="16">
                        <FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Lucida Grande,Helvetica,Arial">
                        <B>&#149;</B>
                        </FONT>
                    </TD>
                    <TD>
                        <FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Lucida Grande,Geneva,Arial">
                        Quit all other applications, since they will run in the background.
                        </FONT>
                    </TD>
                </TR>
                <TR VALIGN="top">
                    <TD WIDTH="16">
                        <FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Lucida Grande,Helvetica,Arial">
                        <B>&#149;</B>
                        </FONT>
                    </TD>
                    <TD>
                        <FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Lucida Grande,Geneva,Arial">
                        Decrease the resolution of the display. The larger the resolution, the lower the performance.
                        </FONT>
                    </TD>
                </TR>
                <TR VALIGN="top">
                    <TD WIDTH="16">
                        <FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Lucida Grande,Helvetica,Arial">
                        <B>&#149;</B>
                        </FONT>
                    </TD>
                    <TD>
                        <FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Lucida Grande,Geneva,Arial">
